{"tid":984634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲豬瘟肆虐　長洲東灣泳灘驚現豬屍　","createTime":"2019-01-17T03:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T03:12:06.000Z","uid":6497,"like":202,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"6ffcd26295ca9aeaa04cbf48a8da4854d0d2eb83","tid":984634,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:14:20.000Z","msg":"長洲東灣泳灘發現豬屍，今早(17日)10時27分，有市民在上址泳灘上，發現一頭約3呎長的豬隻屍體，由於擔心是大陸病死豬隻漂洋過海「登陸」，於是報警，警方正封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n內地非洲豬瘟爆發情況嚴重，曾有24個省份發生過家豬和野豬疫情，累計撲殺生豬91.6萬頭；上月19日，台灣宜蘭縣利澤沙灘亦發現一頭死豬屍體，隨即引起台灣網民恐慌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/photo/bkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190117111135\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190117111135&h=b6734c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fbkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001.html&d=wupA0mMK9VTR1jnO51Ll3tibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=c75c0bef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3c630ffd26b15960c6579d7baa3eafec38ee2a5a","tid":984634,"uid":90820,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de35dd3624e4145a4dad745c36bf2b6967dafeb8","tid":984634,"uid":143241,"like":210,"dislike":2,"score":208,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:17:10.000Z","msg":"封咗個島做疫區好過喇"},{"pid":"62287a0ce17032e782d33da6ce0e5a9252e18b48","tid":984634,"uid":95,"like":189,"dislike":1,"score":188,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:18:37.000Z","msg":"支那又送大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgm